snippet.textDisplay: Hi there everyone.  I am a 66yr old singer?songwriter from Florida.  I met I young man named Zui, about 3yrs ago online. and we have been friends since then. He sent me this beautiful song.  I have never been into this kind of music before, but after this I am serioulsy thinking of maybe buying a cd by these guys. More than just talented musicians.  they are very moving.  I dont know what they are saying, but I certainly doubt that it is violence.  I dont know if I am the only American on here, but I hope it does not matter.  we are all flesh and blood with souls and hearts.  Peace out my brothers and sisters
